    "name": "Hayford", 
    "summary": "<p><b>Hayford</b> is the seat of <a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/House_Hayford\" title=\"House Hayford\">House Hayford</a> in the <a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a>. According to semi-canon sources, Hayford is located half a day's ride north of <a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King's Landing\">King's Landing</a> along the <a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Hayford#cite_note-0\">[1]</a></sup> Hayford sits upon a hilltop and has a stream running alongside the castle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Hayford#cite_note-Raffc27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D-1\">[2]</a></sup> The hidden village of the <a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Lady_of_the_Leaves\" title=\"Lady of the Leaves\">Lady of the Leaves</a> is located near the Hayford road.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"http://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php/Hayford#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D-2\">[3]</a></sup>"
